# Forge identity — copy to repository root as `FORGE_IDENTITY.md`

`ForgeProjectSlug` must be **unique** in your Obsidian vault under `Forge/Projects/`. See THE FORGE kit `docs/KIT_LAYOUT.md`.

```yaml
ForgeProjectSlug: "org-repo-name"
ProjectDisplayName: "Human readable name"
TechStack: "Stack · libraries · datastore"
PrimaryLanguage: "e.g. Python"
DefaultHypothesisType: "Performance"
ForgeSession: 1
RepositoryRoot: ""
ObsidianVaultRoot: ""
```
